    including loss of hosted files.
  </p>

  <h2>Changes to these terms</h2>
  <p>
    We may update these terms as the service changes. Material changes will be announced in the
    project's GitHub repository and reflected in the effective date above. Continued use of the
    service after a change constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.
  </p>

